name: Super Headjump JumpMan
description:
Arrow Keys to move or touch the screen arrows to make JumpMan Move.

Pause the game with the space bar or the Button.

Avoid the falling evil Shroom Men reinforcements will drop from the airplanes.

Jump on top the Shroom Mens heads to destroy them.

( Art , Graphics and Game made over a few couple days by MEDWARDS ART)
